                                    <p>
                                        <seg xml:lang="en">Two joining fragments from a statue base, extensively damaged on all sides. Parts of each surface are preserved, such that it is possible to estimate the overall original dimensions. A substantial part of the front face is preserved, but damaged on all sides except the lower edge. Four Latin letters over two lines and a part of the right marginal moulding are preserved on the rear face from an earlier inscription.</seg>
                                        <seg xml:lang="it"></seg>
                                    </p>
