                                    </rs>
                                    <seg xml:lang="en">Latin text preserved over six lines. Despite the extensive damage around the edges, almost all of the text appears to be preserved, with only a few letters lost from the right margin and at the top corners.</seg>
                                    <seg xml:lang="it"></seg>
